FBIS4-21895 "jptot015__l94060" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 5 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA EGYPT Kuwaiti Reportedly Arrested for Aiding `Militants' Kuwaiti Reportedly Arrested for Aiding `Militants' NC0504202594 Paris AFP in English 1930 GMT 5 Apr 94 NC0504202594 Paris AFP English BFN [Excerpt] Kuwait, April 5 (AFP) -- Egyptian police have arrested a Kuwaiti on suspicion of helping the Islamic militants waging war on the authorities, a source close to the government here said Tuesday [5 April]. He told AFP the man had been arrested last week at Cairo airport in "possession of a large sum of money" and was "suspected of collaborating with terrorist movements in Egypt." The man was an activist of the moderate Islamic Salafiyah group, the source said, without naming him. [passage omitted]
